  <acronym>COMBAT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Non-interventional, Observational, Multi-center Trial to Evaluate Compliance and Efficacy in Mono and Combination Treatment of Candesartan Cilexetil(Atacand)/ Candesartan Cilexetil 16mg, Hydrochlorothiazide 12.5mg(Atacand Plus) in Hypertension</official_title>
