  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate compliance and patients' satisfaction in mono and combination treatment of
      Candesartan cilexetil (Atacand)/ Candesartan cilexetil 16mg, hydrochlorothiazide 12.5mg
      (Atacand plus) in hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
